    "Metadata": {
        "Title": "Bakemono!",
        "Description": "When the Ark Society first settled, a terrible tragedy befell the isle. Cast into the sea was Methuselah Block by trusted colleague Janus, his body disappearing forever while his soul remained.\r\rWith Janus&apos; corpse returned for his funeral wake ceremony, Block animates once more, and you were chosen to assume his corporeal vengeance.\r\rAssume a disloyal form as Janus had, and be reborn as the vindictive obake to eliminate those who wish to immortalize Janus as the hero he proclaimed himself to be.\r\rThis contract was created by a member of the HITMAN community known as Sniff.",
